name: Eyes on me
description:
"Eyes on me, eyes on me, all of them so cold and meaningless, silence me little by little, blind me and gradually take away my color, until I become just empty."

WM. V, digital, 2021, "Eyes in Me" is the first digital art in the collection "Memories of a depleted mind", is a unique and creative view on anxiety and self-sabotage what it is like to live with it and see its intensity, complexity.

"Memories of an exhausted mind" is an invitation to reflection to see the beauty, ugliness, complexity and intensity of an entire universe that we often know little about, ourselves.

2D animation | 2310 x 2664 .mp4  | Duration: 12 seconds | Original Sound |  2021
